    public interface MetadataObject

    Specifies any object holding metadata that could be defined by the SMPTE registration authority and serialised to an AAF file, MXF file etc.. Any class that implements this interface should also be annotated as a media class.

    In the MAJ API implementation of the AAF classes, all interchange objects and meta definitions are metadata objects.

    See Also:
    Forge.make(Class, Object...), MediaClass
